710776f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 45th Street
710776f-a.text:
Twelfth Avenue, north from West 45th Street, showing
the West Side Vehicular Highway under construction.
At this date this is the northerly terminus, tho later
it will be extended.
April 14, 1934
March 20, 1935
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
